{"id":1053579598,"lang":"java","lang_name":"Java","time":"2 months, 2 weeks","timestamp":1695129564,"status":11,"status_display":"Wrong Answer","runtime":"N/A","url":"/submissions/detail/1053579598/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"String to Integer (atoi)","memory":"N/A","code":"class Solution {\n    public int myAtoi(String s) {\n        // removing whitespaces\n        s = s.trim();\n        int n = s.length();\n        if(n == 0) return 0;\n        // System.out.println(s);\n        long ans = 0l;\n        boolean isNegative = false;\n        boolean isMax = false;\n\n        int i = 0;\n        if(s.charAt(0) == '-') {\n            isNegative = true;\n            i++;\n        } else if(s.charAt(0) == '+') i++;\n\n        while(i < n && s.charAt(i) =='0') {\n            i++;\n        }\n\n        while(i < n) {\n            char ch = s.charAt(i);\n            if(ch >= 49 && ch <= 57) ans = (ans * 10) + (long)(ch - '0');\n            else break;\n\n            if(ans > Integer.MAX_VALUE) {\n                isMax = true;\n                break;\n            }\n            i++;\n        }\n\n        if(isNegative) ans *= -1;\n\n        if(isMax) {\n            if(isNegative) ans = Integer.MIN_VALUE;\n            else ans = Integer.MAX_VALUE;\n        }\n        return (int)ans;\n        \n    }\n}","compare_result":"","title_slug":"string-to-integer-atoi","has_notes":false,"flag_type":1}
